                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.48/3828: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Hoover</persName> to the
                        President of Mexico</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ortiz Rubio</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-01-20">January 20,
                            1931</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>It is with the deepest regret that I learn of the recent earthquake in Mexico
                    which has wrought such destruction and loss of life. On behalf of the people of
                    the United States and in my own name, I wish to extend to Your Excellency and to
                    the people of Mexico an expression of sincere sympathy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herbert Hoover</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
